partners.description:
My name is Tea! I am a Shiba Inu!
I like to stream games with friends and my Mama! Sometimes you will hear my puppy Chai on stream when she gets rowdy. She's also a Shiba Inu!
I love reading, I love playing games and I love to have fun! Followers are appreciated and I look forward to streaming with you all!
